WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.240
Hi there! My name is Egils. I am Dance Teacher.

00:00:03.460 --> 00:00:07.580
And today let's talk about Natural Turn in Tango.

00:00:07.820 --> 00:00:11.080
If you want to learn Natural Promenade
Turn 

00:00:11.240 --> 00:00:16.000
and also Natural Promenade Turn followed by Natural Rock Turn

00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:19.100
then stay tuned and watch this video. 

00:00:19.340 --> 00:00:23.880
I will show you these figures with square on the floor, 

00:00:24.040 --> 00:00:27.760
so that you can see very clearly Directions of the Steps.

00:00:28.040 --> 00:00:30.740
Let's start with Natural Promenade Turn.

00:00:30.960 --> 00:00:33.260
Man stars from Promenade Position

00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:43.260
with Left Foot to Side, Right Foot Forward, Left Foot to Side, Right Foot Forward, 

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:49.340
and Left Foot Tap in Promenade Position with stretched Left Toe.

00:00:49.600 --> 00:00:53.720
Now we can continue with Closed Promenade. 

00:00:53.960 --> 00:00:58.020
Slow, Quick, Quick, Slow.

00:00:58.260 --> 00:01:04.620
Lady starts in Promenade Position with Right
Foot to Side

00:01:04.750 --> 00:01:13.190
Left Foot Forward, Right Foot Forward, Left Foot to Side, and Right Foot Tap in Promenade Position.

00:01:13.190 --> 00:01:15.190
Now Closed Promenade

00:01:15.560 --> 00:01:19.480
Slow, Quick, Quick, Slow.

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:30.300
Slow, Quick, Quick, Slow, Slow, Quick, Quick, Slow.

00:01:31.060 --> 00:01:38.060
Now we will dance again Natural Promenade
Turn, but this time we will move diagonally.

00:01:38.450 --> 00:01:43.890
Side, Forward, Side, Forward, and Tap. 

00:01:43.890 --> 00:01:49.030
Now Man continues in this Diagonal, Closed Promenade:

00:01:49.300 --> 00:01:53.380
Slow, Quick, Quick, Slow.

00:01:53.660 --> 00:01:59.800
Lady starts from Promenade Position and also moves in Diagonal:

00:02:00.080 --> 00:02:07.940
Side, Forward, Forward, Side and Tap in Promenade Position.

00:02:08.200 --> 00:02:17.620
And now Closed Promenade in this Direction - Diagonally: Slow, Quick, Quick, Slow.

00:02:18.420 --> 00:02:26.180
Slow, Quick, Quick, Slow, Slow, Quick, Quick,
Slow.

00:02:26.460 --> 00:02:32.660
Let's have look at the Routine: Two Walks,
Progressive Link, Natural Promenade Turn,

00:02:32.900 --> 00:02:35.920
Closed Promenade and Back Corte.

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:43.740
Slow, Slow, Quick, Quick, Slow, Quick, Quick, Slow,

00:02:43.740 --> 00:02:49.960
Slow, Quick, Quick, Slow, Slow, Quick,
Quick, Slow.

00:03:12.580 --> 00:03:19.280
And now I will show you Natural Promenade Turn followed by Natural Rock Turn.

00:03:19.660 --> 00:03:21.640
It's very attractive ending. 

00:03:21.920 --> 00:03:25.900
Man start from Promenade Position, 

00:03:26.220 --> 00:03:28.220
diagonally: 

00:03:29.200 --> 00:03:34.560
Side, Forward, Side, Forward, 

00:03:34.900 --> 00:03:40.980
Back, Forward, Back, Back, Side,
Close.

00:03:41.200 --> 00:03:47.240
Lady Starts from Promenade Position and moves
Diagonally: 

00:03:47.980 --> 00:03:52.840
Side, Forward, Forward, Side,

00:03:53.079 --> 00:04:00.079
Forward, Back, Forward, Forward, Side, Close.

00:04:00.440 --> 00:04:07.180
Slow, Quick, Quick, Slow, Quick, Quick, Slow,

00:04:07.480 --> 00:04:10.080
Quick, Quick, Slow.

00:04:10.380 --> 00:04:13.920
Let's have look at The Routine: Two Walks,

00:04:14.169 --> 00:04:18.689
Progressive Link, Natural Promenade Turn to
Rock Turn.

00:04:18.960 --> 00:04:26.360
Slow, Slow, Quick, Quick, Slow, Quick Quick, Slow

00:04:26.660 --> 00:04:31.480
Quick Quick, Slow, Quick Quick, Slow.

00:04:52.300 --> 00:04:58.620
Let's have look we will dance now both Routines together and with Music.

00:05:37.960 --> 00:05:44.330
I hope this was helpful to you. If you have
some Questions, please put there in Comments.

00:05:44.330 --> 00:05:51.290
I'll be happy to answer your Questions.
And as always thanks for watching, and Happy Dancing!

